  "id": "RAW_a703f8cf",
  "title": "英伟达危！谷歌联手 Meta 要让 TPU 支持 PyTorch，击穿 CUDA 护城河",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI3MTA0MTk1MA==&mid=2652655890&idx=2&sn=f6944a7f263db51b2f07f53b91df2f9c",
  "date": "2025-12-18 06:16:00",
  "author": "新智元",
  "siteName": "新智元",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <h3 data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"246\" data-backw=\"578\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/UicQ7HgWiaUb013ZfdanZicnVwibkWkHEZdtKibadXWP0K6Xgic83InmDjUWUCEegiaq08libLZcNyianfGn4W1dGxrLADA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"247\" data-imgfileid=\"505172192\" data-ratio=\"0.42578125\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cb0e93a0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb013ZfdanZicnVwibkWkHEZdtKibadXWP0K6Xgic83InmDjUWUCEegiaq08libLZcNyianfGn4W1dGxrLADA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <h3 style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">新智元报道 &nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：艾伦</span></span></p>\n  <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></p>\n    <h5 style=\"padding:10px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;word-break:break-all !important;margin-top:10px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">【新智元导读】</span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">谷歌正在推进一项代号为「TorchTPU」的战略行动，核心是让全球最主流的 AI 框架 PyTorch 在自家 TPU 芯片上跑得更顺畅。这项行动不仅是技术补课，更是一场商业围剿。作为 PyTorch 的掌控者，Meta 也深度参与其中，两家巨头试图联手松动英伟达的垄断地位。对于谷歌而言，卖芯片不再是终点，降低开发者的迁移门槛，才是真正介入战争的开始。</span></span></strong></span></h5>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjauhslb4dy\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">谷歌正在发起一项代号为「TorchTPU」的新行动，试图以此打破英伟达在 AI 算力市场的长期垄断。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"285\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"699\" data-imgfileid=\"505172182\" data-ratio=\"0.5076252723311547\" style=\"background-color:transparent;width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1377\" data-width=\"1377\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2e74e59f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb013ZfdanZicnVwibkWkHEZdtMCFNUIYVFuAialHpEQXMEATazDE0fFStveGZA7glyJWoPZvxhBHd6vQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjauhslb1n47\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">据知情人士透露，这项计划的核心在于让谷歌自研的 AI 芯片（TPU）能够更顺滑地运行 PyTorch，这是目前全球最主流的 AI 软件框架。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjauhslbft6\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这是谷歌激进战略拼图中的关键一块，他们希望将 TPU 打造为英伟达 GPU 的有力替代者。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjauhslb1fve\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">随着谷歌急需向投资者证明其巨额 AI 投入的回报能力，TPU 的销售已然成为谷歌云营收增长的重要引擎。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjauhslbye9\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">但光有硬件是不够的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjauhslb1wn6\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">知情人士指出，「TorchTPU」旨在消除那道长期阻碍 TPU 普及的无形围墙，也就是让那些早已习惯在 PyTorch 环境下搭建技术架构的客户，能够无痛迁移到谷歌的硬件上。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjauhslbdf\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">甚至有消息称，为了加速这一进程，谷歌正考虑将部分软件开源。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjauhslbt7q\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">相较于过往对 PyTorch 的零星支持，这一次谷歌投入了前所未有的组织关注度和战略资源。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjauhslb150i\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这一转变的背后，是越来越多渴望采用 TPU 的企业发出的呼声。对他们来说，芯片是个好东西，但软件栈却成了瓶颈。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjauhslb8lf\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">在硅谷，PyTorch 是 AI 模型开发者的通用语言，而它的最大支持者正是 Meta。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjauhslb1kt8\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">在这个行业里，极少有开发者会去为英伟达、AMD 或谷歌的芯片逐行编写底层代码，他们依赖的是像 PyTorch 这样的工具库来自动化处理开发任务。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjauhslb28n\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">自 2016 年发布以来，PyTorch 的成长史几乎就是一部与英伟达 CUDA 生态的绑定史。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjauhslbazx\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">华尔街分析师普遍认为，CUDA 才是英伟达抵御竞争对手最坚固的盾牌。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjauhslboud\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">多年来，英伟达的工程师们不仅造芯片，更致力于确保 PyTorch 开发的模型在其硬件上跑得又快又好。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjauhslb157b\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">相比之下，谷歌此前走了一条截然不同的路。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjauhslbig5\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">他们拥有庞大的内部软件军团，使用一套名为 Jax 的代码框架，并通过 XLA 工具来优化 TPU 的运行效率。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjauhslb1slu\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">谷歌自身的 AI 软件栈和性能优化大多围绕 Jax 构建，这种「圈地自萌」的做法，拉大了谷歌芯片与外部客户实际使用习惯之间的鸿沟。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjauhslbvt0\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">面对路透社的询问，谷歌云发言人虽未对该项目细节置评，但确认了这一战略方向。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 48px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjauhslb8wc\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">他表示，无论是 TPU 还是 GPU 基础设施，需求都在加速爆发，谷歌的重心是提供足够的灵活性和规模，无论开发者选择在何种硬件上构建应用。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">从自用到外售</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">TPU 的角色演变</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjauhslbix8\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">曾几何时，谷歌将绝大多数 TPU 产能视为「私藏珍品」，仅供内部使用。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjauhslb19hu\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这一局面直到 2022 年才发生改变，谷歌云部门成功争取到了 TPU 的销售主导权。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjauhslb8bp\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">此后，谷歌云大幅增加了对外分配的 TPU 额度，试图在客户对 AI 兴趣激增的当下，通过扩大产能和销售来抢占市场。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjauhslb1065\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">然而，供需之间存在错位。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjauhslbyqh\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">全球大多数 AI 开发者使用的是 PyTorch，而谷歌芯片最擅长的却是 Jax。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjauhslb1ydn\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这意味着，想要使用谷歌芯片并获得比肩英伟达的性能，开发者必须进行大量额外的工程适配。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjauhslb22qz\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">在分秒必争的 AI 竞赛中，这种时间和资金的消耗是企业难以承受的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjauhslb1crm\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">如果「TorchTPU」计划成功，它将显著降低企业寻找英伟达 GPU 替代方案时的转换成本。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjauhslbkw\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">英伟达之所以难以撼动，不仅在于硬件性能，更在于 CUDA 生态已经深深嵌入 PyTorch，成为训练和运行大模型的默认选项。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 48px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjauhslbwhu\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">知情人士表示，企业客户曾反复向谷歌反馈，TPU 虽好，但接入门槛太高，因为历史上它强迫开发者放弃通用的 PyTorch，转而学习谷歌内部偏好的 Jax。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">盟友 Meta</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">敌人的敌人就是朋友</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjauhslb1i1g\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">为了加速开发进程，谷歌找来了一位关键盟友，即 PyTorch 的创造者和守护者 Meta。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjauhslb22p2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">据知情人士透露，这两大科技巨头正在商讨协议，让 Meta 获得更多 TPU 的使用权。此前《The Information》也曾报道过这一动向。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjauhslb1oq2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">在早期合作中，谷歌主要以托管服务的形式向 Meta 提供支持。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjauhslb1yvy\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">Meta 使用谷歌设计的芯片运行谷歌的软件和模型，并由谷歌提供运营维护。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjauhslb1hi5\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">对 Meta 而言，推动软件适配 TPU 具有极高的战略价值，它不仅能降低推理成本，更能通过硬件基础设施的多元化来减少对英伟达的依赖，从而在谈判桌上获得更多筹码。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjauhslb1zg\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">Meta 方面对此拒绝置评。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjauhslb91t\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">今年以来，谷歌已开始将 TPU 直接出售给客户的数据中心，而不再局限于自家的云服务。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjauhslb22ll\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">组织架构也在随之调整，谷歌老将 Amin Vahdat 本月被任命为 AI 基础设施负责人，直接向 CEO 桑达尔·皮查伊（Sundar Pichai）汇报。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"374\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"799\" data-imgfileid=\"505172183\" data-ratio=\"0.6658333333333334\" style=\"background-color:transparent;width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1200\" data-width=\"1200\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ea5a9cc9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb013ZfdanZicnVwibkWkHEZdt1Aibokt3NgIia6DDxicpcQicBj6RVgpOuWrOrrtyhwzSQfhMQZr6z7kAjw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjauhslb228n\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这套基础设施对谷歌至关重要，它不仅要支撑包括 Gemini 聊天机器人和 AI 搜索在内的自家产品，也要服务于像 Anthropic 这样依赖谷歌云 TPU 算力的外部独角兽。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\" data-pm-slice=\"3 2 []\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">参考资料：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\" data-pm-slice=\"3 2 []\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/business/google-works-erode-nvidias-software-advantage-with-metas-help-2025-12-17/\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/business/google-works-erode-nvidias-software-advantage-with-metas-help-2025-12-17/</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "谷歌正与 Meta 联手推行“TorchTPU”战略，旨在优化 PyTorch 在 TPU 上的运行效率，以挑战英伟达 CUDA 生态的垄断地位。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "谷歌正与 Meta 联手推行“TorchTPU”战略，旨在优化 PyTorch 在 TPU 上的运行效率，以挑战英伟达 CUDA 生态的垄断地位。",
  "summary": "文章揭示了谷歌代号为“TorchTPU”的战略行动，其核心目标是让业界主流 AI 框架 PyTorch 在谷歌自研 TPU 芯片上更好地运行。此举不仅是谷歌在硬件销售后面向软件生态的技术补课，更是联合 PyTorch 掌控者 Meta，共同削弱英伟达 CUDA 生态护城河的商业策略。文章分析指出，过去谷歌 TPU 虽性能强大，但因需开发者转用 JAX 框架而普及受阻，TorchTPU 计划旨在降低 PyTorch 开发者的迁移门槛。通过与 Meta 的合作，谷歌希望能将 TPU 打造成英伟达 GPU 的有力替代者，为日益增长的 AI 算力需求提供更多选择，并以此推动谷歌云营收增长。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
